  "text": "The (positive) Laplace-Beltrami operator \u2206 on (X \u2022 , g) is essentially self-adjoint on L 2 (X). The spectra of \u2206 consists of essential spectrum [ n 2 [CITATION_1] , \u221e) and finitely many discrete spectrum in (0, n 2 4 ), see for example [CITATION_2] . From the spectral theorem, we know that the resolvent",
